worldofzuul

Class NPCHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • worldofzuul.NPCHolder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Moon, Planet

    public abstract class NPCHolder
extends java.lang.Object
    A super class for Moons and Planets, as they have holding an NPC in common. This class holds the information about which NPC is at what planet. Along with other common attributes, as id, name, pid and description.
